Face Off - Season 5, Episode 00 (Special Preview Episode)




A 2-hour special highlighting the returning Face Off veterans, their past work, their lives since their first turn on the show, and what they hope to accomplish by coming back. Hosted by McKenzie Westmore, this special also features appearances by judges Glenn Hetrick, Ve Neill and Neville Page, who will share their insights into why the contestants were eliminated originally and why they now deserve a second chance.




Original Air Date: 06-Aug-2013
